    <abstract id="aspace_a129e523ef9773c3e9354fe1d7573bfa">Pluto Press gender and sexuality collection consists of 30 files with writings, correspondence, press releases, newspaper and magazine clippings, book covers, contracts, and more between the Pluto Press and authors specialized in gender and sexology, dating from 1982 to 2011. Authors include Judith Rowland, Emmanuel Reynaud, and Bill Marshall. Issues examined include sexual assault and abuse, homosexuality, and sexual identity.</abstract>
